# Welcome to Flounder!
## About
Flounder is an ultra-lightweight platform for making small websites. It uses a new internet protocol called Gemini. Gemini is http as it was in, say, the early 90s: extremely simple, easy to use and understand. There's no tracking, no hidden code that runs in your browser, not even styles! Just lightly styled plain text and files.

To build your site, create a file with a .gmi extension. Flounder will convert these files to html.

