## Links
You can link to other sites using the following syntax:
=> https://gemini.circumlunar.space/ Learn more about Gemini!
=> gemini://gemini.circumlunar.space/ Access the Gemini Network
=> newfile.gmi New File (doesn't exist yet -- try creating it!)

Unformatted text can be displayed like this:
```
In a Station of the Metro
by Ezra Pound

The apparition of these faces in the crowd;
Petals on a wet, black bough.
```

Lists look like this:
* I
* Love
* Flounder!

And quotes look like this:
> To live is to suffer, to survive is to find some meaning in the suffering. - Friedrich Nietzsche

For more information, check out the full Gemini text guide:
=> https://proxy.vulpes.one/gemini/gemini.circumlunar.space/docs/gemtext.gmi

To get started, edit this page! You can also upload files of any type, as long as they're less than 32KB in size. Your site will be live at <your_username>.<domain>
